<section class="market-layout"><article class="card market-card"><div class="market-head"><div class="market-title"><span class="btc-mark">₿</span><div><strong>Bitcoin market</strong><div class="market-sub">Live reference price · 7-day movement</div></div></div><div><div class="market-price" id="btcUsd">Loading…</div><div id="btcChange" class="change">Connecting</div></div></div><div class="chart-wrap"><canvas id="btcChart" aria-label="Bitcoin seven-day USD price chart" role="img"></canvas><div class="chart-status" id="chartStatus">Loading market chart…</div></div><p class="source-note">Market data: CoinGecko · refreshes every 60 seconds</p></article>
